  "detailed_description": "<h1>Our other games</h1><p></p><br><h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Have you ever felt the boundaries between dreams and reality becoming blurred? The main character, Elures, is about to embark on an extraordinary adventure.</i><br><br>Waking up after experiencing amnesia, Elures discovers that she is trapped in the world of her dreams. Your mission is to help her find an escape and in this journey your loyal companion will be her subconscious mind separated from her consciousness. However this dream world is not as simple as it may seem at first glance.<br><br>Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of mystery and unpredictability of this game, where each step reveals new horizons and presents you with complex puzzles. Join Elures and begin your journey towards awakening!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interaction system TouchInput!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/862989c3fcf5db13475111b245cdf974.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/862989c3fcf5db13475111b245cdf974.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/862989c3fcf5db13475111b245cdf974.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of different puzzles!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/79e3bf0201b4251326c7676a4275047e.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/79e3bf0201b4251326c7676a4275047e.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/79e3bf0201b4251326c7676a4275047e.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mini-games</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/c0223b49db43e2f21bcd8903c17d131b.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/c0223b49db43e2f21bcd8903c17d131b.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/c0223b49db43e2f21bcd8903c17d131b.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Change the time around you with an artifact!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/e147cddf16185f5f60a15c57afaadc37.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/e147cddf16185f5f60a15c57afaadc37.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/e147cddf16185f5f60a15c57afaadc37.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Launch a nuclear reactor!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/a2b5c2e2de79776c63755fa22fcb4e05.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/a2b5c2e2de79776c63755fa22fcb4e05.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/a2b5c2e2de79776c63755fa22fcb4e05.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Don't think it will be easy. You will need to configure each reactor component in order to run it. Carefully! The principle of its operation is close to the real one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Reveal the secrets of Isput!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/198deadd981e39819a88a0440b65c9af.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/198deadd981e39819a88a0440b65c9af.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/198deadd981e39819a88a0440b65c9af.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Find all the bones!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/00ab6d91b175a610c7f7592f945c97dd.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/00ab6d91b175a610c7f7592f945c97dd.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/00ab6d91b175a610c7f7592f945c97dd.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Roll the fool!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/dced40d2812775504e446c7c396782df.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/dced40d2812775504e446c7c396782df.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/dced40d2812775504e446c7c396782df.mp4?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features of the gameplay:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You have to face many challenges that are accompanied by unique mechanics and puzzles<br></li><li>Take part in interactive storytelling with an intriguing storyline<br></li><li>Interact with a large number of environment elements<br></li><li>Learn more about the Between universe and its history<br></li><li>Find a lot of references and Easter eggs<br></li><li>And that's not all!</li></ul><br>The further fate of Elures will depend only on you and your attentiveness.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/1c1012134479e9053f307208539870be.poster.avif?t=1707103059\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2279550/extras/1c1012134479e9053f307208539870be.webm?t=1707103059\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://s